---
title: Sesame Crusted Barramundi with Sautéed Zucchini and Butter Soy Sauce
description: Sesame seeds create a gorgeous nutty crunch for this irresistible barramundi recipe. The butter soy sauce gives a lovely sweet and savoury touch that pulls everything together.

